headline: Carrier Honored on Fortune's 2025 Change the World List Changing the World, For the World We Share
summary: During Climate Week NYC, Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, announced it has been named to Fortune's 2025 Change the World list, which recognizes companies delivering positive impact through business strategies.
